1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:11,000
A physical transition can still be the wrong action.

2
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:22,000
Tool-environment common sense is a task constraint.

3
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:33,000
Physical constraints decide what can move.

4
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:44,000
Semantic constraints decide what should move.

5
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:55,000
Semantic manipulation agents encode these role constraints.

6
00:00:55,000 --> 00:01:07,000
The current library is a coverage map, not a complete world model.

7
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:18,000
The next problem is learning controllers for valid transitions.
